videos.headline: Boise State defender picks off Potter at the 49 yard line
videos.description: Kenny Potter pass intercepted Dylan Sumner-Gardner return for no gain to the SJSt 49

videos.headline: McNichols races for 19-yard TD
videos.description: Boise State RB Jeremy McNichols gets to the outside and scores from 19 yards out to give Boise State a 7-0 lead over San Jose State.

videos.headline: Boise State kicker fakes the punt, takes it 29 yards
videos.description: Sean Wale run for 29 yds to the SJSt 34 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Mattison scores on 19-yard run of his own
videos.description: Boise State scores its second touchdown of the game on a 19-yard run, with Alexander Mattison doing the honors this time to extend the Broncos' lead to 14-6.

videos.headline: Potter improvises, hits Johnson for 12-yard TD
videos.description: San Jose State QB Kenny Potter shakes free from Boise State defenders and hits Rahshead Johnson for a 12-yard touchdown to cut the Broncos' lead to 14-13.

videos.headline: McNichols tallies second TD of game
videos.description: Boise State RB Jeremy McNichols finds the end zone for the second time running it in from seven yards out to extend the Broncos' lead to 24-13.

videos.headline: Wilson takes screen pass 15 yards for TD
videos.description: Cedrick Wilson takes the screen pass and bursts 15 yards for the Boise State touchdown to put the Broncos up 31-16 over San Jose State.

videos.headline: Wilson eludes defender, goes 36 yards for second TD of game
videos.description: Cedrick Wilson sheds a defender and runs it 36 yards for his second touchdown of the game to extend Boise State's lead to 38-16.
